		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">gamedude wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">the rom I used did test on a emulator  NESTICLE</div>
<br />That could be a problem. Nesticle is old and buggy, and if the game you are using is an old hack made to work on it, it may not even work on the real console. Try the ROM with recent emulators such as Nestopia and Nintendulator. If it doesn't work on those, it probably won't work on hardware either, which means it's pointless to make a cartridge of it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
